reviews.review_text: It was okay; we were hungry and finally found that place on the google map; then we ordered some food for dinner by machine in the store, it was delicious
Nice work by Harpreet Kaur Gill! I was really craving a hot fudge at like 3 in the morning , she helped us out even though  the system was down. Much appreciated:)

Veneeta staff member at Mcdonald is very happy and nice Lady. She deals with customers happily and her smile makes customers cheerful. She deserves  more than five stars. Mr Gurpreet Singh, Asstt Manager is also friendly and nice person. Works with zeal and passion. I like the way he deals with the customers. Good place to buy junior chicken , coffee, burgers etc.
Best McDonald s in all of the lower mainland. They always load everything right up. I love this McDonald s. I ve never had a bad meal at this McDonald s and they always get my orders right to.
Went there for drive thru , little bit chaotic staff are busy and line is long.  Staff are nice and friendly
Good customer service and staff .This place gets busy but the staff are always their to help.it is a clean restaurant inside and out .awesome service ,keep up the good work .
The space here is very big, and there is a big game field. my daughter likes it very much.

I was here a week ago, a guy named Josh with glasses was helpful when he helped with the Myrewards App to redeem my points all the other managers ignored me but he helped and quickly fixed my issue with the points. The floors were clean and I got my food quickly with no issue!

Good customer service and very quick process. The drive thru is a bit squeezing and tight especially for larger SUVs Food was nice and got what I wanted but the wait period was a bit longer in my opinion
We had such great service and my 5 yr old daughter made 3 new friends in the play~place. Very clean excellent food easy in and out lots of parking

McDonalds is one of the most popular fast-food chains around the world, including Canada, and it is known for its french fries and various menu options. The McDonalds branch located in Guildford mall, Canada, is a typical restaurant, serving the classic McDonalds menu items, including burgers, fries, chicken nuggets, and other fast-food options. Regarding its chocolate donut, McDonalds offers a variety of classic bakery items, such as muffins, croissants, and donuts. Their chocolate donut is one of their popular items and is enjoyed by many customers. Overall, McDonalds Guildford mall is a reliable choice for fast-food options, and their chocolate donut and french fries are worth a try. However, it is also essential to be mindful of ones dietary and health needs while consuming fast foods.
I love Mcdonald coffee   and food theyre affordable.
The Indian girl who is nee is really helpful and hard working there really great service
I ve placed an order thru skip the dishes and i wanted to have some changes in my order so i called at store and the crew member ( Anmol) helped me really well. I like the service.

Every time Ive been to this location the food has been great. The staff were laughing in the back, the managers were kind. Today the manager working the drive thru made us all laugh. Food was quick and hot.

I go here all the time. The daytime staff is awesome and the night staff is a hit or miss not here that I can think of any particular incidents but at the few mcdonalds within my area. But as usual theyve been making great burgers for what 100000 years LOL!!! Anyways if I ever do have any bad experiences I always change the stars accordingly and name the employees whenever possible. Right now its 5 stars meaning excellent staff food and service. So far that is**
I tried the most expensive and famous coffee, but I only enjoy it with McDonalds Dont ask me why even I dont know.
I usually buy coffee drive through, I noticed the staff started to know and when I got to the window almost same person  asian male always in full smile .
It was a great place. I went there with my family include 2 kids. They had so much fun at the play area. Staffs also  so efficient and helpful. Thank you so much for your excellent service.

I spilled my coffee from home just before getting in the drive thru line this morning.... The amazing lady that has worked the pay window for many years, Veneta is her name maybe?? Veneeta??.. Anyway, she went out of her way to get me paper towels to clean myself and my truck before letting me pay for my order. She made a stressful moment much more bareable thank you!!
Fast service, staff was kind, and food was good.
I ordered breakfast here through the Uber eats, Still hot when I got my breakfast.  Btw I would like to say thanks to Gurleen,  he bagged my package perfectly. Food
Fast food fast service tasty hot fare served

The people there are very friendly, tho only thing is that sometimes they are a bit too distracted that they ended up forgetting something on your order, so I always double check to make sure everything is correct. But I always go there.
Food took a little long but workers were extremely nice and it was rush hour so understandable. Manager was apologetic. Appreciated that gesture.

The poor enployees here are overworked . I come here very often and they are alwaya polite and apologetic but in a frenzy. They dont have the right amount of employees maybe but peoples orders get messed up and they have to run out in the rain getting soaked themselves and the food being soaked trying to match up orders all the while hearing people yell at them. Corporate you need to help them out!

Drive thru is great here. I go through at least 3 times a week and get a large double double and on occasion a breakfast sandwich and hashbrown. I generally go incredibly early in the morning and the staff at most drive thrus are usually grumpy and unhappy to be working so early, but not this one! Happy and friendly staff and they always get my order right. No complaints here.
Love how they honor what was emailed to me. Got a free med frozen lemonade in a email but wasnt showing up on my app. Same thing with a mc flurry. They honored it and I left happy.

Best McDonalds in the area. Staff are very friendly. Large, clean, bright room with updated interior. Clean play place with plenty seats inside play area.  With the latest McDonalds self-order machine, you will be able to place order in a minute, grab the tracker, relax and watch your kids playing in the play area. The staff will bring your order to your table when ready. A  life saver when you have kids with you during the rush hour with long waiting line. tip  if you have kids with you, no need to order at the entrance. You can get your kids in the play area first, then use the self order machine right beside the play place and have your order bring the play place. So you always have your eyes on the little ones.

Its a mcdonalds. Can you really right a extended review for McDonalds? Great late night snack for both getting high or just getting hungry. Or a place to bring your kids for a kids meal. Great quick and out. Gotta love McDonalds! Still the best fries Ive ever had.

I had posted a negative review before, but after visiting them every night through their drive thru I had to delete my negative review. Their night staff is great and efficient probably among all the mc Donalds in town at the drive thru for both skip the dishes drivers and customers.
Some branches serve food prepared very well.  I reviewed one about a week ago where the the quarter pounder was terrible, apparently you need to find the good ones.

Was in there the other day getting food and some lady was being rude arguing with how long her McCafee drink was taking. The manager handled it really well and explained that its the machine, that it takes longer and the customer just kept saying no it doesnt, blah blah. The manager handles it really well, and as a former mcdonalds employee I can assure that the McCafee drinks take much longer then normal coffee.  Also the food was awesome- my mcflurry was perfect!

Service was fine. Employees there were polite and patient. Everything was clean and had people cleaning the tables often. The food was good aswell. They didnt mess up my order and the food wasnt stale or over/under cooked. It was perfect.
Big thank you for allowing us to order and service to Semi drivers (BOBTAIL ONLY SIZE)

Peak time, Saturday lunch, 30 plus orders on the back burner, and although the wait is a little longer, as expected, the team here runs well and the young ladies are exceptionally professional for their age. To the older guys swearing at young ladies earning minimum wage, because they have to wait a few extra minutes for their coffee, you should be bloody ashamed of yourselves. Props to these guys and gals, tough job done well. You guys deserve a raise.

Friendly bunch. I drive-thru early in the mornings for tea, and they are nice enough to let it steep for a few minutes before adding cream or sugar, it just tastes a little better that way. I love it.
Great drive through service - especially the mature lady today around noon.  Efficient, courteous, cheerful and a lovely smile.  Thank you and stay safe.

I eat here regularly and have had nothing but friendly service - always with a smile (theyre free you know)!  The food has always been fresh, hot and appealing.  If youre a McDonalds fan, youll like this one!

The manager on shift April 2nd 12:30am short younger lady,  dark skin, long black hair was super sweet, we had an issue with our skip order and went to the restaurant ourselves and had such good customer service, she was super kind and understanding of the situation, was happy to help us and let me rant about how SkipTheDishes sucks and these restaurants take the fall for it she had our food made fresh and even threw in a apple pie, I really really do want to thank her for being super sweet and I think she deserves a raise because that was some of the best service and probably the most happiest worker I ve talked too  :)

Am not fan of fast food restaurant but sometimes coming here to drink tea and to let my kids have a good at play area, Their coffee is not better than Tim Hortons, as you can right now get an extra large for $1, which includes a free refill and one of those stickers for a free coffee, effectively making it about 5 times cheaper than others. Their pastries are also better than tims. Good coupon system too.
Really fresh fries and poutine gravy was so good. Fast service also.
Woah. I love the food here
Love the coffee at McDonalds and. A&W! Im old school and know taste when I taste it! Tim Hortons only puts calories on my butt and costs  more!
My kids love McDonalds. They are fan of their happy meal. They always want to find some new toy in happy meal. Hey... If you are a vegetarian like me , go for burgers with no meat.
Good food. Not might be healthy since its fastfood but it satisfies your hunger. Pretty quick service though it was a busy Saturday lunch time.

One of the best McDonalds Ive been too,they are always fast and know how to make a good burger, when I compare them to the one on 72nd ave, these guys make it right, great job to the staff and the management team, garbage is always thrown out, people do notice and staff is always clean, nice and has common sense
the night staff is very friendly. i do not come often but whenever i come, i do see smiles on their faces for me. #love to be there. #extra quality. #quality maintained.

Ever since the renovations, this place has been top notch by my standards. I come here to work (programmer) and drink coffee. Their coffee is better than Tim Hortons, as you can right now get an extra large for $1, which includes a free refill and one of those stickers for a free coffee, effectively making it about 5 times cheaper than timmies. Their pastries are also better than tims. Good coupon system too.
Good customer service and staff specifically during the night time. The staff is super friendly and i always get fresh food as well as the service is super fast.
One of the best McDonalds Restaurants out there, but of course also depends on the staff out there. Their Guest Experience Leaders were top quality thou
The friendliest McDonalds Ive ever been to. With the new tracker system as well, the staff will bring your food right to your table, saving the trouble with congestion around the counters.
Katrina is an amazing and very friendly manager. She handles questions, suggestions with grace and warmth. Remember, no hashbrowns after 11am!

I have been to the Guildford McDonalds so many times over the years. but never reviewed it. the service is amazing, most of the staff are super nice. the only issue about this McDs is that it tends to get super busy at times. a thousand times better then the Walmart McDonalds across the street.
Hands down the best McDonalds I ve ever eaten. Food was actually hot, and fresh, and they supplied me with plenty of napkins and straws.
Great location. I get my coffees and iced coffees here almost exclusively. McDonalds coffee is the best, there is none like it. Starbucks could use some lessons on how to make a mcchicken.
Egg McMuffin was good,  service is great, homeless person in parking lot hit me up for food and money before I even turned the engine off. Annoying.
Friendly server, first time order maple and cheddar crispy chicken burger. Surprise taste so good. Highly recommend for everyone.
Clean restaurant! Super friendly staff. Best McDonalds Ive been to.
Great service and the food always comes out fast, fresh and hot! One of the better McDonalds Restaurants in Langley BC. Manager does a good job in keeping the restaurant clean.
GREAT, FRIENDLY STAFF AND FAST SERVICE,CANT START MY DAY WITHOUT PICKING UP MY FOOD. I WILL GIVE THEM MORE THAN 5 STARS...GOOD JOB GUYS
Love their drive thru breakfast meal of cheese and egg Mc muffin along with a hot coffee.
My son loves their happy meal. Best part is the toy and the books. Toys pretty cool and big for the price.
Food was good and service was quick. It was raining but they kept the place inside nice and dry .
Very clean and friendly and courteous staff,  fresh food and coffee! Very pleased with Customer Service Excellent! Bravo!
Nice juicy burgers from here today! Had the same burger from a different McDonald s shortly after and the burgers here put the other McDonald s to shame. Thank you :)

The best place in the world! Friendly service even you pay such a little money, perfect sunshine you can enjoy even you pay such a little money, staffs are all kind, warm smile and nice to you even you pay such a little money, you can not find any better place than here unless you pay the real money for what you wish. Cheers!
Everything was quite good as it is on every Mcd. There was no big waiting line
Its really nice the girl name (yuvmavashi )she was nice friendly.we been there for just coffee but then we had food there .nice service clean food clean restaurant and the best thing food get in time
To the employee who proclaimed McDonalds is the greatest restaurant on earth, please never change
Veneeta C. is a guest experience leader at McDonalds and I found her to be super friendly and always smiling.  I just wanted to say thank you to her.
Very clean everything is spaced out properly and the manager was extremely nice..couldnt be more helpful. Thanks and the food was hot...
Best coffee going. No wonder Timmys is now 7th in Canada. They have way better coffee at McDonalds for same price.
Newly renovated, looks great! Always good service and friendly staff. PS. Drive through is fast most of the time.
I use SkipTheDishes from this Location usually in the midnight. Always fresh food and well packed. Thanks for working guys ;)
This is my favorite McDonalds in Surrey.  I have 3 near me and this one wins for overall service.  No comment on the food.  Its McDonalds!
Waited almost 10mins only for an order of 2 small coffee frappe... tasted awful. Very disappointed
this was the best McDonalds restaurant I have ever been to. Great customer service, fast workers, very nice people, and great food.
The ladys here were very nice. One lady offered to carry my food to the playroom for me because my hands were full.
Best mcdonalds ever... crew was so kind and welcoming... food was served hot and fresh! Must try there maple chedar crispy chicken!
Table service! I was there the day they started this - its a great addition to McDonalds.  I like the more health conscious and flavourful menu.
This is nice and large McD in Surrey.  Lots of seating.  Good service. And lots of parking .  very convenient.
Got my food from a manager named Destiny, she was amazing! Great service and food was fresh!
I like the guy who says welcome to the greatest restaurant on earth
Anmol is really great! She provided excellent service.
I have always loved MacDonalds and have many memories with my kids and now my grandchildren
I had a fun night here and made a big mess whilst throwing food at my father and siblings. It was a fun night about a 9/10
Good doesntt suit it at all it was more then good it was astounding it has delicious food and amazing staff 5 stars from me
I grab my morning coffee here sometimes. The drive thru is always quick and Im greeted with a smile.
Quick and easy on the run and this particular store is usually quite a bit faster then most.
At this location the people are super nice they have super etiquettes how to tag their safety empty and theyre super nice
Love the chicken mc muffin..yum
The food is superb the one who is serving us was not.
Always good, quick food grab, druce thru option is so efficient with kids.
Despite being insanely busy, they gave great service and quality very quickly
Quick and fast, easy bites
Quick, friendly and and your orders are always right....   to this location
Very fast and good customer service
Lots of spaced out seating, prompt friendly service
This location seems to have the fastest drive through and most courteous staff!
